blueprint.label: Science
blueprint.description:
90 SPM  of seven fundamental science packs.

This is a final build.  It'll eventually be presented as a series of blueprints that starts simple and grows to this end version.

After build, all chests in the train yard must be MERGED.

Step 1: iron plates, copper plates, and some wood in a chest.  Build only a couple yellow & red pack assemblers.
